Our Partner
Aroga Technologies signed a strategic agreement with Aroga Holdings Corp, a research, development and manufacturer company focused on developing products and strategies to maximize the social contributions of people with disabilities. Aroga Holdings Corp’s purpose is to achieve this goal through the development of intellectual property (IP) and product manufacturing for non-traditional education markets. Aroga is a Canadian Google Apps reseller, with this Aroga has the ability to provide services for Google Apps for Education and Google for Work. As a google Apps for Education Reseller, We can provide support for the Aroga Academy a (virtual school). 
 
DEEP AND COMPREHENSIVE EXPERIENCE. GLOBAL RELATIONSHIPS. PROVEN RESULTS.

To put it simply, Soellingen’s consultants have a single goal of providing expert financial, operational, managerial and strategic financial advice to entrepreneurs, small and mid-sized companies, as well as, not-for-profit organizations, and government agencies wishing to reach the next level.


Whether your company in its early stages or well-established, we will help you assess and implement the strategy that is right for you:


If profitability needs to be increased, we examine your internal and external processes and procedures to find the stumbling blocks that are impeding your growth and work with you to make the changes needed to improve your bottom line.
If your organization needs to raise capital, we will get you the funding you need from the public or private source that is best for you.
If you are unsure about how to move forward in a new market, we will help craft and implement a marketing plan that takes into account your target market’s business and cultural norms.


Our consistently reliable, high-quality service helps clients generate consistent revenue, operating margins, earnings and cash flows.














































