 Wear it.

Our disposable, real-time, quantum-infused holograms are a cutting-edge wearable technology that delivers a wide range of benefits to the body. Simple to use and discreet, the hologram discs are a safe and effective do-it-yourself way of providing energy, relief, balance and overall wellness through holographic accupressure. 
Simply wear them daily or as needed, and experience what thousands of people around the world are touting as “the next big breakthrough in wellness”. Click the button below to learn more about this technology and our 3 unique products: Real-Time Relief™, Real-Time Energy™ and Real-Time Sleep™.

